
== mod_gacl Apache module ==

This Apache module is an extension of the module mod_auth_script,
written by Shigeru Kanemoto <sgk@ppona.com>,
-- Accense Technology Inc. (http://accense.com/)

The module should be used together with mod_dav and mod_ssl. With these
three modules you will have a file server with directory permissions set
via GACL.

The GACL code is taken from gridsite (http://www.gridsite.org/),
-- Copyright (c) 2002-7, Andrew McNab, University of Manchester

A simple Makefile is provided for building as DSO module. On most Unix-like
system, you will type just like below:

    % make
    % su
    # make install

For more information, see the code.